<h2 id="0"><a class="local" href="#I.0" title="anchor"></a>Canon Ptolomei et Pictagore<span class="note"><a aria-label="1" class="note txt" href="#n1"></a><small class="note" data-sign="1" id="n1"> Pictagore<span class="txt">]</span> Pytagore <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> de diversis eventibus secundum naturas planetarum</h2>
<h3 id="I.1"><a class="local" href="#I.1" title="anchor"></a><span class="txt">⟨1⟩</span> </h3>
<p>Inventum Ptolomei et Pictagore,<span class="note"><a aria-label="2" class="note txt" href="#n2"></a><small class="note" data-sign="2" id="n2"> Pictagore<span class="txt">]</span> Pytagore <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> secundum naturas planetarum subtilissima doctrina conpilatum, hoc etiam ‘monama<span class="txt">[</span>r<span class="txt">]</span>chia’<span class="note"><a aria-label="3" class="note txt" href="#n3"></a><small class="note" data-sign="3" id="n3"> monomarchia<span class="txt">]</span> m…chia (<i class="txt">unclear</i>) <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> nuncupatur. Et dicitur a ‘monos’, quod est ‘unum’, et ‘machia’,<span class="note"><a aria-label="4" class="note txt" href="#n4"></a><small class="note" data-sign="4" id="n4"> machia<span class="txt">]</span> marchia <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> quod est ‘pu<span class="txt">[</span>n<span class="txt">]</span>gna’, id est pu<span class="txt">[</span>n<span class="txt">]</span>gna unius ad unum. Danda est igitur a nobis regula archanissima, divinissima et perfectissima, cuius <u class="num">lectore</u><span class="note"><a aria-label="5" class="note txt" href="#n5"></a><small class="note" data-sign="5" id="n5"> lectore<span class="txt">]</span> lectori (?) <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> carente iudicamus esse ineptum. Regula est in qua laboravit satis Pictag<span class="txt">⟨oras⟩</span><span class="note"><a aria-label="6" class="note txt" href="#n6"></a><small class="note" data-sign="6" id="n6"> Pictagoras<span class="txt">]</span> Pytagoras <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> et Ptolomeus. Hanc Alexander Magnus<span class="note"><a aria-label="7" class="note txt" href="#n7"></a><small class="note" data-sign="7" id="n7"> Alexander Magnus<span class="txt">]</span> Magnus Allex<span class="txt">⟨ander⟩</span> <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> secum habuit<span class="note"><a aria-label="8" class="note txt" href="#n8"></a><small class="note" data-sign="8" id="n8"> habuit<span class="txt">]</span> propter habuit <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> in omni suo discursu per orbem, per hanc sibi prospera futura vel adversa previdens cuncta subegit, omnia subiecit. Mir<span class="txt">[</span>i<span class="txt">]</span>um quod una regula te instruit totum quod sum dicturus. Si eger recubuerit, restitutionem eius vel occubitum certissime pensabis; in pugna duorum, utrum victurus sit manifeste loqueris; fratres duos aut sorores aut coniugatos, statim dum nomen sciveris; de morte aut vita, utrum victurus aut moriturus sit<span class="note"><a aria-label="9" class="note txt" href="#n9"></a><small class="note" data-sign="9" id="n9"> victurus aut moriturus sit<span class="txt">]</span> victurus sit aut moriturus <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> explorabis; negotium bene vel male die hac vel illa, immo<span class="note"><a aria-label="10" class="note txt" href="#n10"></a><small class="note" data-sign="10" id="n10"> immo<span class="txt">]</span> ymo <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> hora diei, inceptum significare poteris; et multa alia que enumerare non est opus. Numeros itaque subscribimus profundissima disciplina et scientia inventos, numeros dico omnium litterarum et omnium planetarum. Et nomina earum vel eius de quo queris suppotato vel subputatis<span class="note"><a aria-label="11" class="note txt" href="#n11"></a><small class="note" data-sign="11" id="n11"> subputatis<span class="txt">]</span> supputatis <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> et facta summa utriusque per 7 vel per<span class="note"><a aria-label="12" class="note txt" href="#n12"></a><small class="note" data-sign="12" id="n12"> per<span class="txt">]</span> <i class="txt">om.</i> <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> 9 divisione, per regulas subscriptas quotus quodcum<span class="note"><a aria-label="13" class="note txt" href="#n13"></a><small class="note" data-sign="13" id="n13"> quotus quodcum<span class="txt">]</span> quottus quottum <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> vincat numerum ad inferiora recurrendo invenies. Si ergo fuerit negotium unius, numerum nominis sui cum numero stelle que tunc principatur coaptabit<span class="note"><a aria-label="14" class="note txt" href="#n14"></a><small class="note" data-sign="14" id="n14"> coaptabit<span class="txt">]</span> <i class="txt">om.</i> <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> diligenti inquisitione, et numquam<span class="note"><a aria-label="15" class="note txt" href="#n15"></a><small class="note" data-sign="15" id="n15"> numquam<span class="txt">]</span> nuncquam <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> te fallet. Numerum ergo<span class="note"><a aria-label="16" class="note txt" href="#n16"></a><small class="note" data-sign="16" id="n16"> ergo<span class="txt">]</span> <i class="txt">om.</i> <i class="txt">P</i></small></span> nominum propriorum et elementorum statim collocemus.</p>
